To install any rpm with no dependency
  $ sudo rpm --install diffmerge-4.2.0.*.rpm
To install any rpm with dependencies  <------------ Use YUM
  $ sudo yum install diffmerge-4.2.0.*.rpm
To delete rpm package
  $ sudo rpm --erase diffmerge
